00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,629
* Shoot 'em 'fore they run now

16
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,116
* Do the jerk, baby

17
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,910
* Do the dirty now

18
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:33,196
* Put on your high-heel shoes

19
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:37,635
* l said we're going down here
listen to 'em play the blues

20
